              <div class="bg-catppuccin-surface0 p-6 rounded-lg border border-catppuccin-surface1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-catppuccin-text mb-2">Software Engineer</h3>
                <p class="text-catppuccin-subtext1 font-medium mb-2">Previous Roles</p>
                <p class="text-catppuccin-subtext0 mb-4">
                  Experience in software development, working on various projects and technologies 
                  before moving into leadership roles.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="bg-catppuccin-peach/20 text-catppuccin-peach px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Development</span>
                  <span class="bg-catppuccin-red/20 text-catppuccin-red px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Problem Solving</span>
                  <span class="bg-catppuccin-yellow/20 text-catppuccin-yellow px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Technology</span>
